name: Devin Nunes
speech: Mr. NUNES. Madam Speaker, unfortunately, I was detained and unable to  cast my vote for the two amendments and passage of ", H.R. 8294, ", the  National Apprenticeship Act. Had I been present, I would have voted in  the following manner ``nay'' on rollcall No. 225, ``yea'' on rollcall  no. 226, and ``nay'' on rollcall No. 227.
